                  <summary>Copy of a letter written by Sarapion, a member of the First Friends and a dioiketes (or hypodioiketes), concerning a death and, it seems, subsequent division of a kleros.  The document also mentions a scribe of the Machimoi whose name no longer survives.</summary>
